Navy 1903:
xzgamer55012/30/23
Patrol Boats: 10
xzgamer55012/30/23
Patrol Boats: Lightly armed vessels that won’t fair very well against an actual navy and usually are used for anti-piracy and such. They use steam boilers and usually can travel up to speeds of around 15 to 20 mph. They usually stay in port most of the year as the ocean is frozen over and the nation lacks coal deposits so it doesn’t wish to use its limited reserves.
